title: Ukraine launches counteroffensive against Russia as troops engage in intense fighting
description: Counteroffensive action against Russian forces is under way, Ukraine president Volodymyr Zelenskyy has said, with troops engaged in intense fighting along the front line.

title: Man breaks record for amount of time spent living underwater
description: A man who spent 100 days living underwater at a Florida Keys lodge for scuba divers has resurfaced.

title: At least five killed in blast at rocket and explosives factory in Turkey
description: An explosion at a rocket and explosives factory has killed five workers in Turkey, its defence ministry has said.

title: Colombia plane crash: What we know so far as children rescued after five weeks
description: In the deep depths of a Colombian jungle, four children have been found alive weeks after a deadly plane crash.

title: British girl stabbed in France knife attack 'able to leave hospital in coming days'
description: A three-year-old British girl who was stabbed in a knife attack in the French Alps will be able to leave hospital in the coming days, prosecutors have said.

title: Four children found alive - five weeks after a deadly plane crash
description: Four children have been found alive - five weeks after the plane they were travelling in crashed into thick jungle.
